data.description:
DON’T MISS OUT ON THIS OPPORTUNITY OWNING RANCH STYLE SF RESIDENCE THAT COME WITH NEWER SOLAR PANELS .Well maintained home, offers three bedrooms, one full bathroom, lovely sun room, 2 car garage with a 2 car covered carport.  Interior features 720 sqft of living space. Flooring contains carpet, linoleum, and SOLAR PANELS were installed in November 2021, and the new owner will own the solar panels. Never pay another electricity bill again. Excel energy will send the owner a bi-monthly rebate check in the amount of $110-$120 every other month because they collect an excess of energy from this home. 
Upon entering you'll find a lovely eat in kitchen, spacious living room, with ceiling fans for comfort. The property is heated with forced air and natural gas and cooled with evaporation cooling, wood floors. Exterior features, 0.16-acre lot with a fully fenced
yard, offering privacy and security. 2 vehicle over-sized garage and a 2 vehicle carport. This property is located in Adams County, offering easy access to local schools, including Monaco Elementary, Adams City Middle/Junior School, and Adams City High School.
